name: Execute Playbook using Mock Data
description:
This reference block showcases an example of configuring a playbook where you can add sample data and execute a playbook step mocking the sample data as output.
Note: To enable Mock Output, set variable value `useMockOutput` as `true`

Example: You might want the playbook, that mocks output for malicious IP Addresses from Virustotal.

arguments.name: VirusTotal
